event.description: Mouse event recorded on the <svg/> element.

renderer.description: The type of renderer to use for the scatter plot. - svg-single: Renders every scatter item in a <circle /> element. - svg-batch: Batch renders scatter items in <path /> elements for better performance with large datasets, at the cost of some limitations. Read more: https://mui.com/x/react-charts/scatter/#performance
